
                          Tatool

  What is it?
  -----------

  Tatool is an open-source training and testing tool for psychological experiments.

  Documentation
  -------------

  The most up-to-date documentation can be found at http://www.tatool.ch/.

  Release Notes
  -------------

  The full list of changes can be found at http://www.tatool.ch/.

  System Requirements
  -------------------

  JDK:
    1.6 or above
  Memory:
    No minimum requirement.
  Disk:
    No minimum requirement. The local database size depends on usage.
  Operating System:
    Operating system has to support Java 6.

